- On "Skip": call onComplete() and close modal immediately
  ingredient exists in DB with 0 stock
- On "Cancel" in step 1: close modal, reset form
- On "← Back" in step 2: go back to step 1 with fields pre-filled
- Reset all state when modal closes

Use Tailwind only. Match MenuFormModal visual style.
Dark overlay, white card, max-w-lg, centered.

